'''利德贺市场'''（Leadenhall Market）位于[[伦敦市|伦敦市]]的[[恩典堂街|恩典堂街]]，是伦敦最古老的市场之一，历史可追溯到14世纪。其所在地正是古罗马时期伦敦的中心<ref name=City>[http://www.cityoflondon.gov.uk/things-to-do/visiting-the-city/food-drink-and-shopping/leadenhall-market/Pages/default.aspx ''Leadenhall Market''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cityoflondon.gov.uk/things-to-do/visiting-the-city/food-drink-and-shopping/leadenhall-market/Pages/default.aspx |date=20121031042951 }} ([[City_of_London|City of London]]) accessed 30 September 2009</ref>。

利德贺市场拥有华丽的天花板，漆成绿色，枣红色和奶油色，因而也是一个旅游景点<ref name=City/>。1972年列为二级[[登录建筑|登录建筑]] <ref name=Listing>{{Cite web|url=https://britishlistedbuildings.co.uk/101286182-leadenhall-market-with-subsidiary-numbering-langbourn-ward|title=Leadenhall Market with Subsidiary Numbering, City of London, London, London|first=Good|last=Stuff|website=britishlistedbuildings.co.uk|accessdate=2020-08-01|archive-date=2020-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820125425/https://britishlistedbuildings.co.uk/101286182-leadenhall-market-with-subsidiary-numbering-langbourn-ward|dead-url=no}}</ref>。  

在一些电影中，利德贺市场被用来代表伦敦。
